===Definitions===
{{zh-hanzi}}

# to [[be called]] 
#: {{zh-usex|你 '''叫''' 什么 名字？|What is your name?}}
#: {{zh-usex|這 '''叫''' 什么？|How do you '''call''' this? / What '''is it called'''?}}
# to [[call]], to [[name]]
#: {{zh-usex|我們 經常 '''叫''' 他 的 綽號|We often '''call''' him by his nickname.}}
#: {{zh-usex|我 可以 '''叫''' 他 ^@戴夫 吗？|May I '''call''' him Dave?}}
# to [[call]] {{qualifier|someone}}
#: {{zh-usex|叫 警察|to call the police}}
#: {{zh-usex|要是 需要 什么，我 就 '''叫''' 你。|I' ll '''call''' you if anything is needed.}}
# to [[cry]], to [[shout]]
#: {{zh-usex|狗叫|bark}}
#: {{zh-usex|她 高興 地 '''叫''' 起來，投入 了 她 母親 的 懷抱。|With a '''cry''' of joy, she fell into her mother's arms.}}
# to [[hail]], to [[greet]]
# to [[ask]], to [[order]]
#: {{zh-usex|'''叫''' 他 待 在 家裡。|'''Ask''' her to stay home.}}
#: {{zh-usex|醫生 '''叫''' 他 休息 幾 天。|The doctor '''told''' him to lay off a couple of days.}}
# to [[hire]], to [[call]] {{qualifier|a taxi}}, to [[order]] {{qualifier|in a restaurant, in a shop}}
#: {{zh-usex|我 給 你 '''叫''' 什么 菜？ 肉 排 還是 魚？|What shall I '''order''' for you? Steak or fish?}}
# {{non-gloss definition|(used in a passive sentence to introduce the agent)}} [[by]]
#: {{zh-usex|莊稼 '''叫''' 大水 沖 跑 了。|The crops were washed away '''by''' the flood.}}

====Usage notes====
* {{sense|to call, to be called}} when used for a person, 叫 refer to surname and / or name.

